posting_body: ['AMC-', 'CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants- BRE #01449928', 'CHAPARRAL APARTMENTS IN PALMDALE, CA', "PALMDALE'S MOST LUXURIOUS COMMUNITY . . .", 'CHAPARRAL.', 'Surround yourself with resort-style landscaping and the finest amenities to help you escape from the hectic pace of everyday life.', 'Our professional management staff goes the extra step to provide you with most comfortable living experience.', "Plus, Chaparral's prime location puts you minutes from the freeway, restaurants and the Antelope Valley Mall.", 'Come to the best address in town!', 'Security deposit', 'Studios $1,000 OAC, One Bed $1,200 OAC, Two Bed $1,500 OAC.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 125', 'OR Text', '125', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Follow The Link', 'Below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 974 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Extended closets', '- Air Conditioning', '- Central Air', '- Built-In Microwave', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Private Balconies/Patios', '- Window Covering', '- Dishwasher', '- Large Bedrooms', '- Pet Friendly (up to 2 pets 25Lbs or less)', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Fireplace', '- View', 'Community Amenities', '- Covered Parking', '- Swimming Pool', '- Public Transportation', '- Easy Freeway Access', '- Laundry Facility', '- Business Center', '- Tennis Court', '- Small Dogs Allowed', '- Cats Allowed', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Allowed: Small Dogs and Cats', 'Driving Directions', '14 Freeway north to Palmdale Blvd.', 'Exit left.', 'Proceed to 5th Street West.', 'Turn left.', 'Property is on the right.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Sunday: 12:00PM-6:00PM', 'Chaparral Apartments', '38441 5th St. West, Palmdale, CA, 93551', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'wzcKO0nDWXa5']
